  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/gaming/\" rel=\"tag\">游戏产品</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/13/steams-user-tags-feature/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/785b3c4338e402599eca8f9de382cfdd/boreale-steam-lead.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n显然，在 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/steam\">Steam</a> 看来光有游戏分类还不足以满足玩家搜索游戏时的需要。在最新版的 Steam 客户端中，开发团队加入了最新的游戏标签功能，让用户可以在产品页面内为任意作品加上自己认为合适的标签。至于其用途，自然就是方便其它玩家搜索，比如说，目前已经有人为「CoD: Ghosts」加上了「垃圾（garbage）」的标签，想要玩的朋友记得三思而后行啊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/02/13/steams-user-tags-feature/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://www.joystiq.com/2014/02/12/steam-tags-help-you-find-games-based-on-custom-criteria/?ncid=rss_truncated\" target=\"_blank\">Joystiq</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/tag/\" target=\"_blank\">Steam</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/13/steams-user-tags-feature/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20829663/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/13/steams-user-tags-feature/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
